OL,3,CWelsh National Opera 'pause' strikes
OL,4,Cover jobs and pay
OL,6,FPlanned strikes by members of the
OL,7,Fchorus at the Welsh National Opera
OL,8,F(WNO) will be "paused" following talks
OL,9,Fin a dispute over cuts.
OL,11,FEquity said strikes planned for
OL,12,FSeptember 21 and 29 will not go ahead
OL,13,Ffollowing "productive discussions"
OL,14,Fwith WNO management over the past week.
OL,16,FA strike on 18 October remains in
OL,17,Fplace and action short of a strike
OL,18,Fwill still be taken by chorus members
OL,19,Fthroughout the season as originally
OL,20,Fplanned.
