OL,3,CWelsh National Opera 'pause' strikes
OL,4,Cover jobs and pay
OL,6,FEquity said: "A deal has not yet been
OL,7,Freached and despite pausing strike
OL,8,Faction at this time, the chorus
OL,9,Fcontinue to be concerned about the
OL,10,Fimplications and any implementation of
OL,11,Fmanagement's current proposals.
OL,13,F"The pause will allow time for further
OL,14,Ftalks to take place with the hope of
OL,15,Freaching an agreement with WNO
OL,16,Fmanagement which addresses core
OL,17,Fconcerns over job losses, pay cuts and
OL,18,Fcompulsory redundancies."
