OL,3,CWelsh National Opera 'pause' strikes
OL,4,Cover jobs and pay
OL,6,FSimon Curtis, Equity Wales official,
OL,7,Fsaid: "We're encouraged by recent
OL,8,Fpositive engagement from WNO
OL,9,Fmanagement so far, which is why our
OL,10,Fmembers made the decision to pause
OL,11,Fstrike action. However, we are not out
OL,12,Fof the woods yet and an agreement
OL,13,Fensuring the jobs and livelihoods of
OL,14,Fthe chorus has not been reached."
